{"tid":81510,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養隻柴犬，有野想請教巴打","createTime":"2017-01-15T11:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T15:23:55.000Z","uid":67570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2e8bc752203cb115c75f1eab349a6673cbe451","tid":81510,"uid":67570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"1. 領養好d定係買好？ (本人想領養)<br />\n2. 如果帶埋佢去跑步，佢頂唔頂得順？ <br />\n3. 佢難唔難教？驚佢係屋內亂痾同亂吠。 <br />\n4. 佢甩毛勁唔勁？ <br />\n問住咁多先，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceab10a37d2ffdc43af6cd89297cf748668cf90b","tid":81510,"uid":67570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSsaJw8gnedsuiaPKWdqrCqposDTeQi6H5GPgBCGZh8eg?filename=134e800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F134e800.jpg&h=3fa0f699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"539be85b52cbab3a4830f5e766cc4fb4d136d996","tid":81510,"uid":67570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSsaJw8gnedsuiaPKWdqrCqposDTeQi6H5GPgBCGZh8eg?filename=134e800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F134e800.jpg&h=3fa0f699&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70b56615f0b30e67a817c25cf9b4326643d32dc4","tid":81510,"uid":38320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"難教"},{"pid":"a5cb4edf7600aa4ecd95bb493fcaf249698abc27","tid":81510,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 領養好d定係買好？ (本人想領養)<br />\n領養啦，但可能要等，唔係話有就有<br />\n2. 如果帶埋佢去跑步，佢頂唔頂得順？ <br />\n佢會跑得快過你，佢地天生係短跑爆發去獵食<br />\n佢地無慢跑呢樣野<br />\n3. 佢難唔難教？驚佢係屋內亂痾同亂吠。 <br />\n狗難唔難教同隻狗無關，同個人有關<br />\n推薦你睇dog whisperer <br />\n你會學到好多有關教狗既知識<br />\n4. 佢甩毛勁唔勁？ <br />\n問住咁多先，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會甩，一轉天氣就甩<br />\n朋友個隻一年兩次"},{"pid":"1c32078790fbe54a7812edca842eda2f3be4db29","tid":81510,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"如果你第一次養狗<br />\n就更建議你領養啲成犬（超過一歲）<br />\nBb既柴犬係最撚麻煩最撚惡搞"},{"pid":"ef97b4b18fb4cb2aeeb9037600a232f4965b2b7f","tid":81510,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"好難教"},{"pid":"90cfc78c45af94979d4155657320aa3f8c456b1f","tid":81510,"uid":67570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T11:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f324636009cb4660d92e1971178804517fdfafe9","tid":81510,"uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:41:31.000Z","msg":"有人話難有人話易。愛佢就要付出。無話因為難教就唔養。"},{"pid":"ea8ba228409d2059495f72ab5ba2adacc39079d5","tid":81510,"uid":50508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSsaJw8gnedsuiaPKWdqrCqposDTeQi6H5GPgBCGZh8eg?filename=134e800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F134e800.jpg&h=3fa0f699&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n順便講句，領養有呢個質素？邊有可能。"},{"pid":"babba3ac78708c0a6899360334fc72f575f49e2c","tid":81510,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:47:23.000Z","msg":"柴犬係特別難教 我覺得<br />\n由細開始教佢定點痾屎尿會容易d<br />\n80%柴犬都唔放得繩 因為一放就走叫極都唔會返主人度<br />\n除非幾歲大隱定d就可能可以放到繩"},{"pid":"172b97d8f80798d54bd723b5d57367255f183dcf","tid":81510,"uid":22141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"仲有柴犬甩毛係超級勁 基本上一年四季都甩緊毛<br />\n冬天轉夏天甩得更加多 因為佢會由兩層毛變返一層毛"},{"pid":"bb84ab345aab8c98fe8710b15e9088cc293581e5","tid":81510,"uid":14083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 領養好d定係買好？ (本人想領養)<br />\n2. 如果帶埋佢去跑步，佢頂唔頂得順？ <br />\n3. 佢難唔難教？驚佢係屋內亂痾同亂吠。 <br />\n4. 佢甩毛勁唔勁？ <br />\n問住咁多先，thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. Up to you<br />\n2.得，佢地唔係貴婦個d,我驚跑到你驚左<br />\n3.好撚難<br />\n4.一開始會，愈大愈小<br />\n<br />\n養緊"},{"pid":"0eee2968f282e49f4480c279bb114ad15b9df8bb","tid":81510,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"柴犬超難教超曳<br />\n唔岩新手養<br />\n養之前諗清楚先"},{"pid":"2be431e95157e8e987ba77564b9cde27bb9f7236","tid":81510,"uid":46838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:48:14.000Z","msg":"同堆柴犬啲脾氣差，出街你預左同唔到其他狗玩/夾"},{"pid":"60023bb53318abac8ce0c60a6eece1caa530023a","tid":81510,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？"},{"pid":"76403e789660342e4be9aab0841edc1ef313fc4b","tid":81510,"uid":18286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？</blockquote><br />\n同問 哥基呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e46c09c65bd99e9bf69b246c6c4403667903551","tid":81510,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"柴犬難d有得領養喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b904bab7968cd9c5ac394e67d789509e9d25a4bb","tid":81510,"uid":14083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一隻狗就係柴犬，而加都係得一隻，我覺得最重要係陪佢行街，食野就我食乜佢食乜，薯片都比佢食，當佢唐狗咁養，因為佢地同唐狗都無乜分別，身體好好"},{"pid":"5c3c99deef828e662c6d77495d5557001a642ec0","tid":81510,"uid":14083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一隻狗就係柴犬，而加都係得一隻，我覺得最重要係陪佢行街，食野就我食乜佢食乜，薯片都比佢食，當佢唐狗咁養，因為佢地同唐狗都無乜分別，身體好好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呀嫲養過雪橇同德國狼狗，喂d野仲癲，食剩所有野加狗糧，養到一隻16，同一隻15歲，隻雪橇企起身差唔到175好大隻唔肥，咬死過無數野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係我個陣負責帶佢哋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到老左都無病無痛咁死，不過有好大個backyard 比佢地玩"},{"pid":"1e7531c701c20d5c602678a00a11473c9367a3b1","tid":81510,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"好多柴可以領養 , 留意下Fb, <br />\n俾啲耐性, <br />\n唔好買啦 <br />\n我都好後悔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗到我隻柴萬千寵愛, <br />\n但係佢親生父母名都無, 就好內疚<br />\n<br />\n今日通過住家繁殖牌呢啲on9惡法, <br />\n只會令呢啲事無日無之"},{"pid":"673b6f0ca42ebb02d962e0963ba36dbe6629ef24","tid":81510,"uid":61181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有柴犬甩毛係超級勁 基本上一年四季都甩緊毛<br />\n冬天轉夏天甩得更加多 因為佢會由兩層毛變返一層毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要頂得順呢樣 ,<br />\n啲毛係多到你想像唔到"},{"pid":"162caca6ec9f5dff6b19681397daef0949f3b609","tid":81510,"uid":16683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴絲既柴犬係邊度買/領養？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ba4eaefb78dd31916b897715a662fa34df7037","tid":81510,"uid":61922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？</blockquote><br />\nFrd有養哥基<br />\n成日吠好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要成日帶佢跑街<br />\n甩毛撚<br />\n新手勿養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adf399a9ceb9c7a8972cc3a3d34b58ba3686188","tid":81510,"uid":13309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來柴犬咁惡教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 哥基？</blockquote><br />\nFrd有養哥基<br />\n成日吠好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要成日帶佢跑街<br />\n甩毛撚<br />\n新手勿養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果隻無吠但好有活力，如果你鍾意行山啊果啲帶埋佢消下體力相處下都幾好<br />\n哥基都幾多毛甩要日日sor毛但其實幾分鐘搞掂，最緊要多啲同佢玩囉"}]}